---
layout: relation
title: 'expl:pass'
shortdef: 'reflexive pronoun used in reflexive passive'
udver: '2'
---

Reflexive pronouns (see the feature [cs-feat/Reflex]()) are used in various constructions in Pomak,
including so-called _reflexive passive._

